result.name: Pastel Pink Sky - Roblox
result.description:
This is a follow-up to a request, I fulfil most, so go ahead and describe the pic you want in the comments or send an imgur link to it. If you find a better-quality image put an imgur link to it in the comments. 

Original image from Newgrounds artist unknown and they deleted the original, an archive link to the original is found in the code. 

This code was created by me, do give feedback for improvements in the comments. If you want more fixed roblox styles just click BoopBop at the top, or you can click DittoDino below for some mediocre youtube progressbars.
result.notes: This is the Alt of DittoDino. Disclaimers: Tablets/iPads or phones won't work, Chrome & Opera are the only browsers that work well with the extension. Press 'Read more' for further help. Help Sections Links Below. English Help Section. Turkish Translated Help Section - Yardım bölümü Türkçe'ye çevrildi. French Translated Help Section - Section d'aide traduite en français - cliquez ici. Russian/Cyrillic Translated Help Section - Русский/кириллица переведенный раздел помощи - кликните сюда. Spanish Translated Help Section - Sección de ayuda traducida al español - haga clic aquí. A disclaimer: all the translations I make are just Google translated, I ain't no multilingual savant, so if there are any readers who are proficient in the languages above, please do tell me where I've messed up. 10 June 2023 - Released. 12 August 2023 - Tried to make a more readable text colour.
